{"tid":1250218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線支援、流動物資、緊急救護專屬群組","createTime":"2019-06-22T04:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:18:38.000Z","uid":264368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"671c365cffbeee75c3b583b52f11261e7a395e02","tid":1250218,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>香港民眾防衛隊 Hong Kong Civil Defence Force</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">本平台設立前線支援、流動物資、緊急救護專屬群組，讓欲參與救援行動的人士自由提供或接收群組專屬或跨群組之情報，改善行動前計劃與行動中協調的討論及溝通，以促進救援行動之效率。<br />\n<br />\n加入本平台群組的組員可自由行動，亦可根據行動前計劃或行動中協調之情報自行決定是否提供相關協助。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>平台各群組目的如下:</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">前線支援，協助撤退，處理催淚彈，調配物資及救傷。<br />\n流動物資，協助物資站，或根據情報前往前線提供物資。<br />\n緊急救護，協助救護站，或根據情報前往前線救傷。<br />\n情報發佈，協助群組傳達求助至其他群組，或於本平台頻道上公佈最新消息。<br />\n媒體發佈，協助情報群組於社交媒體上轉載或發佈防衛及救援資訊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>填寫以下表單加入:</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://forms.gle/eXCEqNBJaG6QQUuC7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FeXCEqNBJaG6QQUuC7&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=a356f51e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/eXCEqNBJaG6QQUuC7</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong>聯絡資訊:</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Telegram Channel: <a href=\"http://t.me/HKCDFInformation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKCDFInformation&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=16013d5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKCDFInformation</a><br />\nTelegram Contact: <a href=\"http://t.me/HKCDF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKCDF&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=5105ac3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKCDF</a><br />\nInstagram Page: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/civildefenceforcehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fcivildefenceforcehk&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=173335dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/civildefenceforcehk</a><br />\n<br />\n**加入本平台群組需透過Telegram Secret Chat閱後即焚功能，檢查學生證/工作證以驗證身份。</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"843a4b2216bf2dbe3d0ab50da800328a6fdb0135","tid":1250218,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:52:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e510ff3454af2497a5f0e6bbf756941239ed15ba","tid":1250218,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:39:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"afce14e85aef0b053e418660fde900304419c71e","tid":1250218,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:28:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0321c801f92ae694dbf382f0e4a7eaaa43ddea4d","tid":1250218,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d5d6af4c490ac22acb8f003366ee507e9afd449d","tid":1250218,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:34:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a4cadd664ff5b04c9355833965f6935fc5f070eb","tid":1250218,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:04:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d4eebbc1fab8ad8368997011888cb829d04b0a05","tid":1250218,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:32:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"30242ba9a37df5801835bbe30ff6609319f1da21","tid":1250218,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:35:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fa9f0d28c0228575d605935d49e122ed24d8740f","tid":1250218,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cd4f21690a5b66470020446cce65800856f85508","tid":1250218,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"06142fbfda418a24d4c0458b34c1b831da